mata\" class=\"alert alert-warning\">\n            Presenza gi√† confermata\n          </div>\n          <div v-else>\n            <p class=\"check-text\">I dati sono corretti?</p>\n            <button class=\"btn-confirm\" @click=\"confermaPartecipazione\">\n              Conferma Presenza\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<style scoped>\n.area-convalidatore {\n  min-height: 100vh;\n  background-color: #f5f7fa;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n}\n\n/* HEADER */\n.header {\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 800px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\nh2 {\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #0C2B4E;\n  font-size: 1.8rem;\n}\n\n.logout-btn {\n  background-color: #dc3545;\n  border: none;\n  color: white;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  padding: 8px 14px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background-color 0.25s ease;\n}\n\n.logout-btn:hover {\n  background-color: #c82333;\n}\n\n/* LOGIN CARD */\n.login-card {\n  margin-top: 60px;\n  background-color: white;\n  padding: 40px;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 400px;\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.input-group {\n  width: 100%;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  margin-bottom: 18px;\n}\n\n.input-group label {\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #0C2B4E;\n  margin-bottom: 6px;\n}\n\n.input-group input {\n  border: 1px solid #ccc;\n  border-radius: 6px;\n  padding: 10px 12px;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  transition: all 0.2s;\n}\n\n.input-group input:focus {\n  outline: none;\n  border-color: #0C2B4E;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(12, 43, 78, 0.3);\n}\n\n.form-text {\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  color: #666;\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.btn-primary {\n  background-color: #0C2B4E;\n  border: none;\n  color: white;\n  padding: 10px 26px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background-color 0.25s ease;\n}\n\n.btn-primary:hover {\n  background-color: #174170;\n}\n\n/* SCANNER */\n.scanner-section {\n  margin-top: 40px;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n/* PARTECIPANTE CARD */\n.partecipante-card {\n  background-color: #1D546C;\n  color: #fff;\n  margin-top: 40px;\n  padding: 30px;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 500px;\n  box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);\n}\n\n.partecipante-card h3 {\n  font-size: 1.4rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.nome {\n  font-size: 1.3rem;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-bottom: 6px;\n}\n\n.presenza {\n  margin-top: 25px;\n}\n\n.check-text {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n}\n\n.btn-confirm {\n  background-color: #3CB371;\n  color: white;\n  border: none;\n  padding: 10px 24px;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  transition: background-color 0.25s ease;\n}\n\n.btn-confirm:hover {\n  background-color: #2e8b57;\n}\n\n/* ALERT */\n.alert {\n  padding: 12px 18px;\n  border-radius: 6px;\n  background-color: #ffcc00;\n  color: #222;\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n  .login-card,\n  .partecipante-card {\n    width: 90%;\n    padding: 25px;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.5rem;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n\n<script>\nimport jsQR from 'jsqr';\n\nexport default {\n    name: \"ApriFotocamera\",\n    data() {\n        return {\n            stream: null,\n            qrContent: \"\",\n            scanning: false,\n        }\n    },\n    emits: [\"emitQRCode\"],\n    async mounted() {\n        \n    },\n    methods: {\n        async apriFotocamera() {\n            try {\n                this.scanning = true;\n                \n                this.$nextTick(() => {\n                    this.scanQR();\n                })\n\n                this.stream = await navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({\n                    video: {facingMode: \"environment\"}\n                });\n                this.$refs.video.srcObject = this.stream;\n                \n            } catch(error) {\n                console.error(error)\n            }\n        },\n        async scanQR() {\n            const video = this.$refs.video;\n            const canvas = this.$refs.canvas;\n            const ctx = canvas.getContext(\"2d\");\n\n            const scan = () => {\n                if(!this.scanning) return;\n\n                if(video.readyState === video.HAVE_ENOUGH_DATA) {\n                    canvas.width = video.videoWidth;\n                    canvas.height = video.videoHeight;\n                    ctx.drawImage(video, 0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);\n\n                    const imageData = ctx.getImageData(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);\n                    const code = jsQR(imageData.data, imageData.width, imageData.height);\n\n                    if (code) {\n                        this.$emit(\"emitQRCode\", code.data);\n                        this.scanning = false;\n                        this.stopCamera();\n                    }\n                }\n\n                requestAnimationFrame(scan);\n            }\n\n            scan();\n        },\n        stopCamera() {\n            if (this.stream) {\n                this.stream.getTracks().forEach(track => track.stop());\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    beforeUnmount() {\n        this.stopCamera()\n    }\n}\n</script>"],"mappings":";;AA0PA,OAAOA,IAAG,MAAO,MAAM;AAEvB,eAAe;EACXC,IAAI,EAAE,gBAAgB;EACtBC,IAAIA,CAAA,EAAG;IACH,OAAO;MACHC,MAAM,EAAE,IAAI;MACZC,SAAS,EAAE,EAAE;MACbC,QAAQ,EAAE;IACd;EACJ,CAAC;EACDC,KAAK,EAAE,CAAC,YAAY,CAAC;EACrB,MAAMC,OAAOA,CAAA,EAAG,CAEhB,CAAC;EACDC,OAAO,EAAE;IACL,MAAMC,cAAcA,CAAA,EAAG;MACnB,IAAI;QACA,IAAI,CAACJ,QAAO,GAAI,IAAI;QAEpB,IAAI,CAACK,SAAS,CAAC,MAAM;UACjB,IAAI,CAACC,MAAM,CAAC,CAAC;QACjB,CAAC;QAED,IAAI,CAACR,MAAK,GAAI,MAAMS,SAAS,CAACC,YAAY,CAACC,YAAY,CAAC;UACpDC,KAAK,EAAE;YAACC,UAAU,EAAE